 - File transfer support (drag and drop for desktop)
 - Text chat sessions
 - Document configuration changes required to make it work with local SylkServer instance
 - Show Preview window when join a conference from link, Press continue if microphone works
 - Audio indication when the conference start (2nd party joins the conference the first time)
 - Auto login on start or after failure to register
